description:
Emily shares her secret for successful relationships & marriage– spend time apart. She supports marriages where couples have healthy communication, tell each other what they want in bed, and travel to remote areas of the globe… separately. Emily breaks down Skype Sex and e-humping etiquette. How to direct a Skype scene and act in it as well. Emily and Menace discuss the top fantasies for men and women and the likelihood they will actually come true. Emily also answers listeners questions: Orgasm denial, advice for lesbians, how long should you wait to have sex, and how do you tell someone they’re bad in bed?

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
